snippet.title: Trailer - Imperivm RTC - HD Edition "Great Battles of Rome"
snippet.description:
Now on Kickstarter: https://cutt.ly/ixX7gs5
Make the new Imperivm HD become a reality!!!

Imperivm "Great Battles of Rome", the "Old school" Real-Time Strategy blockbuster from Haemimont Games and FX Interactive, is back... And now in HD!!!

The new Imperivm HD doubles down on a terrific single and multiplayer gameplay created together with the ImperivmWorld Gamers Community.
